name: Disco Filet - Alpha
description:
Disco Filet - Alpha Ever wanted to play Five Finger Filet to music? Part of the GMTK Game Jam.

Available currently on Mac as an alpha build. Oh the bugs you will see!

Playtime: 1 minute

Beats: 1,2,3,4,5,6
Menu: Mousey Click

Created by a single person Jam team. There will be bugs, but hopefully this will be fixed in future versions.
